%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Vigilance Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing upon the powers of law and justice, the vigilance
domain specializes in both investigating activities and
rewarding those who do right while punishing those who
are found to be in the wrong.

The vigilance domain contains the following spells:
Orders Oath (2nd), Mark of Justice (5th), Weighed in the Balance (8th)

Divine Favor, Orders Oath, Heroism, Vicarious View, Vigilance, Inspiring Recovery, Greater Heroism, Frightful Aspect*, Overwhelming Presence

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kreysneothosies

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
